Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.34,中文,,0,0,0,,几周之前 一个隐形的穹顶从天而降\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A few weeks ago, an invisible dome crashed down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.37,中文,,0,0,0,,罩住了彻斯特磨坊镇 把我们和外部世界隔绝开来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on Chester's Mill, cutting us off from the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.26,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶是怎么来的 其中蕴含着什么奥秘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why the dome is here or what mysteries lie ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.99,中文,,0,0,0,,每一天都试探着我们的底线\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Every day it tests our limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我们内心深处的善与恶 一览无余\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}bringing out the best and the worst in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.99,中文,,0,0,0,,有人说我们会永远被困在这里面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Some say we'll be stuck here forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:25.99,中文,,0,0,0,,但是 我们决不放弃 坚持寻找逃出穹顶之法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but we will never stop fighting to find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:28.09,中文,,0,0,0,,大吉姆把蛋扔下了悬崖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}REBECCA: Big Jim threw the egg off the cliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我想这证明了蛋就是穹顶的能源\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'd say that proves it's the dome's power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.20,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶在收缩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome's contracting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:32.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你是说它缩小了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You mean, it's shrinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我计算了穹顶收缩的速度\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}REBECCA: I figured out that at its present rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.31,中文,,0,0,0,,再过不久 穹顶就会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it won't be long before the dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:37.38,中文,,0,0,0,,- 把我们完全压扁 - 这一切都是你的错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Crushes us completely? - All of this is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:38.92,中文,,0,0,0,,- 梅勒尼在哪 - 我画了一副景象\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Where's Melanie? - I painted a vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.64,中文,,0,0,0,,可能指示了我们救她的方法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it may show us how to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.86,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼 梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - Melanie! Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:44.12,中文,,0,0,0,,抓住我的手 抓住我的手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Grab my hand! Grab my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:45.82,中文,,0,0,0,,- 在我的梦里 我看到梅勒尼消失了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- In my dream, I saw Melanie disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:47.89,中文,,0,0,0,,- 可我不知道原来预示那个样子 - 我爱你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- but I didn't know it meant that. - I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:52.74,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.74,中文,,0,0,0,,因为她就该跟我在一起 吉姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}'Cause she's supposed to be with me, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:04.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须去找梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We have to go after Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:06.91,中文,,0,0,0,,太危险了 大家哪也不许去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's too dangerous. No one's going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:09.98,中文,,0,0,0,,- 能看到什么吗 - 看不到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Can you see anything? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:12.17,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天啊 又是一次地震\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, my God! There's another earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:18.27,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得这个坑通向哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where do you think the crater leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.14,中文,,0,0,0,,也许这是另一个隧道 就像学校里那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe it's another tunnel, like at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:22.51,中文,,0,0,0,,- 可能通往顶点镇 - 也可能通往别的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It could lead to Zenith. - Yeah, or somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:24.27,中文,,0,0,0,,只要是外面 什么地方都行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anywhere but here would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一定要搞清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've got to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:29.79,中文,,0,0,0,,但我们一定要想好怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But we've got to do it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.88,中文,,0,0,0,,决不能让任何人冒生命危险\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}not risking anyone else's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.04,中文,,0,0,0,,救命 救命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Help me! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:37.30,中文,,0,0,0,,- 波林 波林 - 让她侧躺下来 轻一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Pauline, Pauline! - Lay her down on her side, gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:38.26,中文,,0,0,0,,亨特 需要你的衬衫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hunter, I need your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.37,中文,,0,0,0,,- 怎么回事 - 是莱尔 莱尔捅了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What happened? - Lyle. Lyle stabbed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.99,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那他去哪儿了 - 他死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Where is he now? - He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.34,中文,,0,0,0,,给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我试过给她止血了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I tried to stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:47.72,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们的急救设备都放在学校\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- All our medical supplies are at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:48.76,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们现在就过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Well, let's get there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.52,中文,,0,0,0,,普瑞斯就在树林边上 我们走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The Prius is at the edge of the woods. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.93,中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:52.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:55.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我被捅了之后 我看到了一副景象\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}After I was stabbed, I had a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.84,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶选择了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.99,中文,,0,0,0,,但 不止你一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But... you're not alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.11,中文,,0,0,0,,还有一个人 但我看不到他的脸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}there's someone else, but I can't see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:07.46,中文,,0,0,0,,他自己不知道自己是选中的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He... he doesn't know he's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:14.82,中文,,0,0,0,,快 拿担架来 把担架放到她的下面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, get a stretcher! Let's get this underneath her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.42,中文,,0,0,0,,一定要压住她的伤口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got to keep pressure on this wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:18.13,中文,,0,0,0,,- 瑞贝卡 你也跟我们一起来 - 好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Rebecca, you're coming with us. - Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:20.14,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了 准备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- BIG JIM: Yeah. Yeah. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:21.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你会没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:23.25,中文,,0,0,0,,- 来 - 一 二 三 起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Come on. - One, two, three... up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.25,中文,,0,0,0,,保持呼吸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:31.99,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:34.30,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶越来越近了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The walls are getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.72,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶是半球形的 它水平方向和垂直方向\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome's a sphere, it's contracting horizontally
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.57,中文,,0,0,0,,都在收缩 我觉得穹顶在回缩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- and vertically... - I think it's shutting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.27,中文,,0,0,0,,在里面的所有东西都会被压成泥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everything inside's going haywire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.78,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我们要找个传送装置 下到坑里探个究竟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, we've got to get some gear, so we can explore this crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:45.76,中文,,0,0,0,,救命 救命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Help! We need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.80,中文,,0,0,0,,从蒂尔登农场传来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's near the Tilden farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为所有人都去镇中央了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought we got everybody in the middle of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.81,中文,,0,0,0,,一定是汤姆回来拿什么东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tom must have gone back for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.65,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 看好亨特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, keep an eye on Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.98,中文,,0,0,0,,别做任何蠢事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.35,中文,,0,0,0,,- 等等 你去哪里 - 我们要去找台笔记本电脑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Wait, where are you going? - JOE: We need to get a tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:00.14,中文,,0,0,0,,- 用来干什么 - 坑出现之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What for? - When this thing opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.46,中文,,0,0,0,,可能在穹顶里制造了一个新的裂缝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it might have created a new crack in the dome,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.12,中文,,0,0,0,,意味着我们也许能收到外面的WiFi信号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}which means we may be able to get a Wi-Fi signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我们也许就能和戴安娜的爪牙取得联系\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe we can get a message to the Hounds of Diana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:07.13,中文,,0,0,0,,如果爪牙们说梅勒尼就在顶点镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If the Hounds tell us that Melanie's in Zenith,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.13,中文,,0,0,0,,那说明那个坑正是通往外界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that means the crater's our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:14.61,中文,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.18,中文,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.46,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了 - 地震了 这东西塌下来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What happened? - The shaking! It fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.76,中文,,0,0,0,,- 压到了我的腿 - 救救我爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It's crushing my leg! - Help my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.73,中文,,0,0,0,,- 把他带走 把我儿子带出去 - 求你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Get him, get my son out of here. - Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:25.52,中文,,0,0,0,,- 不 我也要帮忙 - 和茱莉亚走吧 儿子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- No, I need to help! - Go with Julia, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.61,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你也要跟我们一起走 - 汤姆 我会照顾他的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You're coming with us! - Tom, I'll look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.61,中文,,0,0,0,,把他带出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get him out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我们试试这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:35.02,中文,,0,0,0,,- 孩子 跟茱莉亚走 - 我不会丢下你的 爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Buddy, go with Julia. - I'm not leaving without you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.82,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们会救他的 好吗 - 我在试试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- We're gonna help him, all right? - I'll try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.99,中文,,0,0,0,,走 出去 走 出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go! Get out! Go! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:43.63,中文,,0,0,0,,- 不要 爸爸 不要 - 走 快走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- No, Dad, no! - Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.76,中文,,0,0,0,,- 不 爸爸 爸爸 不 不 - 我觉得乔伊是对的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- No, Dad! Dad, no! No! - I think Joe's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.34,中文,,0,0,0,,- 穹顶在闭合\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- that the dome's shutting down. -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我想我们只剩几个小时了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm guessing we've got a few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.97,中文,,0,0,0,,- 不 爸爸 不 - 来吧 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- No! Dad, no! - Come on, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.97,中文,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸 - 我懂 孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Dad! - I know, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:57.22,中文,,0,0,0,,我们走 快 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Let's go, come on, guys. -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.92,中文,,0,0,0,,把所有纱布都找来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get as much gauze as you can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.47,中文,,0,0,0,,放在这儿 放在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Put over here! Put over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.06,中文,,0,0,0,,她的腹部很僵硬 内出血了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her abdomen's rigid... she's bleeding internally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:06.29,中文,,0,0,0,,莱尔可能捅到了某个器官 可能是肾脏 也可能是肝脏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Lyle might have lacerated an organ. Kidney, maybe, or her liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.55,中文,,0,0,0,,山姆 我知道你能就她 做些什么 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sam, I know you can help. Do something, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.11,中文,,0,0,0,,要做手术来给她止血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's gonna need surgery to stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.23,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好 那快做啊 无论 - 我不是外科医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Well, then, operate. Do whatever... - I'm not a surgeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:12.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我们没有麻药和设备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And we don't have anesthesia or equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.52,中文,,0,0,0,,没有核磁共振 我连是伤到哪个器官都不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't even tell which organ is injured without an MRI.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:16.99,中文,,0,0,0,,- 听着 肯定有办法的 快想办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Listen, there is an answer... - Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.95,中文,,0,0,0,,- 求你 你一定要救救她 - 我会想尽一切办法的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Please, you have to help her. - I'm doing everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.20,中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:34.94,中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.23,中文,,0,0,0,,没有信号 很遗憾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No signal. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.71,中文,,0,0,0,,不过这是个好主意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was a good idea, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.55,中文,,0,0,0,,那 说明这个坑没有在穹顶里弄出裂缝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, the crater didn't create a crack in the dome,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.10,中文,,0,0,0,,也就没有新的隧道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and there's no new tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.52,中文,,0,0,0,,也许有 但信号被谁屏蔽了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe it did, but somebody's blocking the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.23,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 也许是个混蛋杀人犯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, or maybe it's just a giant, killer suckhole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:59.99,中文,,0,0,0,,再有几个小时我们就要被压扁了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're literally hours from being crushed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.53,中文,,0,0,0,,也许我就该去找我妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe I should just go find my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.16,中文,,0,0,0,,和她一起度过最后的这几个小时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and spend my last few hours with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.90,中文,,0,0,0,,而不是在这儿说服自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}instead of trying to convince myself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.37,中文,,0,0,0,,那些控制着穹顶的王八蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that whoever or whatever controls this dumb dome...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.70,中文,,0,0,0,,会顾忌我们的死活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}even gives a crap about any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.96,中文,,0,0,0,,诺瑞 我需要你镇定下来 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Norrie, I need you here with me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.98,中文,,0,0,0,,-嘿 嘿 你要干什么 -执行B计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Hey. Hey, wh-what are you doing? - Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.99,中文,,0,0,0,,乔伊 你不能下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Joe, you're not going down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.99,中文,,0,0,0,,这是属于我的镇 现在也是你们的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is my town... yours, too, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.13,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们不做些什么 我们都活不了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If we don't do anything, we all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.29,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们探一探这个坑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If we explore the crater,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.33,中文,,0,0,0,,那样我们也许能救出所有人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then we might be able to find a way to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.33,中文,,0,0,0,,他说得对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我们比别人更了解穹顶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We know the dome better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事了 波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're okay, Pauline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.87,中文,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.87,中文,,0,0,0,,莱尔要把你从我身边夺走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Lyle tried to take you away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.15,中文,,0,0,0,,他捅了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He stabbed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不过他已经死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But he's dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:56.02,中文,,0,0,0,,一切都会好的 我保证\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everything's gonna be okay, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我们能给她止痛吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can we give her something for the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我们有吗啡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've got morphine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.70,中文,,0,0,0,,只能用十毫克 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just ten milligrams, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.29,中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.30,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我们谈谈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We should talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.65,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我马上回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.99,中文,,0,0,0,,她看起来不错 在好转\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She looks good... on the mend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.47,中文,,0,0,0,,内伤太重了 不做手术无法控制\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The internal damage is too massive to control without surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.60,中文,,0,0,0,,那再想想别的办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, do something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我能让她尽可能感到舒服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can keep her as comfortable as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.77,中文,,0,0,0,,但我实在无能为力给她止血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but there is nothing I can do to stop her from bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你什么意思 她会死吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you saying, that she's gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:38.99,中文,,0,0,0,,如果还有什么办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If there was something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.99,中文,,0,0,0,,任何办法 我都会去试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}anything, I would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我无法接受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.18,中文,,0,0,0,,波林是回来救我们的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pauline came back to save us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.32,中文,,0,0,0,,而不是在儿子面前失血而死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}not bleed out in front of her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.42,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶不会让她就这么死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome won't let her die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:55.65,中文,,0,0,0,,这是对她的另一个考验\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is just another test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我的家庭 我的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My family, my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.95,中文,,0,0,0,,都是被穹顶选中的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we were chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:05.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一定要把妈妈送到坑那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've got to get Mom back to the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.76,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼不是凭空消失的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie didn't just disappear into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.19,中文,,0,0,0,,坑一定是通往什么地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It must lead somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我也希望如此 朱尼尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I hope it does, Junior,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.57,中文,,0,0,0,,但波林的伤太重了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but Pauline's injuries are too severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.99,中文,,0,0,0,,如果再去动她 会使失血加速的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If we move her, it will accelerate the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.50,中文,,0,0,0,,那么 告诉我们能做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, tell me what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.64,中文,,0,0,0,,- 她需要增加体液 - 哪里有盐水\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- She needs fluids. - Where do I get saline?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.82,中文,,0,0,0,,- 诊所 - 我去找\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- The clinic? - I'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.62,中文,,0,0,0,,这是另一个隧道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It is another tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:26.43,中文,,0,0,0,,但和学校下面的那个不一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But it's different than the one underneath the school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.32,中文,,0,0,0,,那些是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.78,中文,,0,0,0,,不过很酷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but they're cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.30,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 还有点吓人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, and kind of terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.30,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们接着走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.60,中文,,0,0,0,,希望我们能在这下面找到梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I hope we can find Melanie down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.21,中文,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.23,中文,,0,0,0,,来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗 妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You okay, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.79,中文,,0,0,0,,就有点痛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just a little pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我们能再给她注射一点吗啡吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can we give her... some more morphine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.99,中文,,0,0,0,,不行 再注射就要过量了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We don't want to give her an overdose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.87,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 朱尼尔 没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, Junior, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:26.16,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸马上回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dad's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:29.37,中文,,0,0,0,,好吗 我们会治好你的 就像梅勒尼那样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay? And we're gonna fix you up... just like Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:32.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得她没事吗 她逃出去了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you think she's okay? That she made it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.09,中文,,0,0,0,,什么事都有可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:39.87,中文,,0,0,0,,把我的画笔和画布拿过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My brushes and canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.79,中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我也许能画出我们出去的路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe I can paint the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.94,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔 这很重要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior, it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.02,中文,,0,0,0,,快去拿过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now go get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.87,中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}James.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:55.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一起经历了这么多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've been through so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:04.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我一定会看着我的小甜心 成长成一个男子汉的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I got to see my sweet, sweet boy become a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:14.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你 妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.94,中文,,0,0,0,,永远\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.99,中文,,0,0,0,,永远\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你和朱尼尔说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What you said to Junior...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:33.70,中文,,0,0,0,,像是永别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it sounded like a good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都了解事实\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We both know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:39.35,中文,,0,0,0,,-我活不下去了 -我们只需要让你稳定下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I'm not going to make it. - We just have to get you stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.56,中文,,0,0,0,,如果那个陨石坑是出口，我们会带你出去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If the crater's a way out, we'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.99,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.16,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶已经处置完我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome's done with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我自己会死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I saw my own death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.27,中文,,0,0,0,,波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pauline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.99,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔才是关键\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All that matters is Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.73,中文,,0,0,0,,他要活下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That he survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.41,中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆不愿意放弃我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And Jim won't let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想那样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.34,中文,,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.35,中文,,0,0,0,,让我安详的去吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let me go peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.25,中文,,0,0,0,,贝姬 帮我吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Becky, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.85,中文,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为你出现就为了这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think you were supposed to be here for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我要去拿点装备 回到陨石坑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've still got to go grab that gear, get back to the crater,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.46,中文,,0,0,0,,看看下面是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}figure out what's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我们应该分头行动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We should split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我带艾丹回学校 你继续去坑那边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll take Aidan back to the high school, while you head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.99,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 在学校等我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, wait for me at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.61,中文,,0,0,0,,找山姆要一个对讲机 我们保持联系\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right? Grab a walkie from Sam. I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:37.09,中文,,0,0,0,,宝贝 我们从这边走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, honey, we're gonna head this way, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.64,中文,,0,0,0,,岔口要怎么走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do we do about this fork?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:44.99,中文,,0,0,0,,哪一边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.61,中文,,0,0,0,,看 乔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Joe, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我们走哪边了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think we just made our decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得这个坑会开多长时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How long do you think the crater's gonna stay open?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:07.36,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道 应该不长吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I-I don't know. Not long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须去告诉芭比这里有可能是一个出口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've got to tell Barbie there might be a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:26.74,中文,,0,0,0,,快点 诺瑞 快点 乔 我们快走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on Norrie Come on Joe Come on let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.39,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你们特么觉得自己在干哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.39,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们下去了 -废话 我看到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- We went down. - Yeah, I-I see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:43.03,中文,,0,0,0,,不要做蠢事 这五个字你们不懂么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What part of "Don't do anything stupid" Did you not understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.84,中文,,0,0,0,,不要生气 我们不能等了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't be pissed. We couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我们发现更多的隧道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We found more tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.14,中文,,0,0,0,,那里还有一直帝王蝶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There was a Monarch down there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.43,中文,,0,0,0,,给我们指了一条尽头有光的道路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It-it showed us a path... with a light at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你看到它去哪了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you see where it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.87,中文,,0,0,0,,里面一切都在摇晃 我们必须出来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We had to get out, things are shaky down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.59,中文,,0,0,0,,通道不会开太长时间的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The passage may not be open for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:56.87,中文,,0,0,0,,这肯定是通向某个地方的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But it goes somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.11,中文,,0,0,0,,就像我之前说的 任意地方都比这儿好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And, like I said before, anywhere's better than here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你老头好像\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It doesn't look like your
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.76,中文,,0,0,0,,不会再送蛋来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}dad's showing up with the egg anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:05.28,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶收缩的间隔时间越来越短了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The time between its contractions is getting shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.39,中文,,0,0,0,,而且连带的让天气越来越糟了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And the dome's making the weather worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.19,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们去坑底下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, well, we're going down the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.18,中文,,0,0,0,,这是唯一选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's our only shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.83,中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还有一个出路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think we got another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.03,中文,,0,0,0,,有可能出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This might be the way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.02,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.54,中文,,0,0,0,,山姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:23.02,中文,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.69,中文,,0,0,0,,那个坑有可能是出路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The crater could be the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:26.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我们快去聚集镇里的所有人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've got to gather the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.78,中文,,0,0,0,,好的  所有人不是在这边就是在蔷薇酒吧那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, well, most everyone's either here, at the Sweet Briar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.59,中文,,0,0,0,,-还有教堂 -好的 那就赶紧把大家聚集起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- or the church. - All right, well, round them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:32.83,中文,,0,0,0,,-让所有人去树林 -怎么去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- We've got to get everybody to the woods. - How?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.66,中文,,0,0,0,,额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.32,中文,,0,0,0,,搭校车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}school buses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.92,中文,,0,0,0,,校车是用柴油的  这里有很多游艇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They run on diesel. There's a whole fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.39,中文,,0,0,0,,把艇里的柴油加到校车里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got to be fuel left in some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我去看看 把伤患聚集起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll check it out. Round up the wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们先让他们上车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we'll get them on first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:44.14,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 不能坐车的 就走过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, anyone who can't fit on the buses will just walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.90,中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆 你在干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.39,中文,,0,0,0,,在找生理盐水 有人受伤了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm looking for saline, someone's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.92,中文,,0,0,0,,额 你听到计划了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}W-Well, didn't you hear the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要离开了 所有人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're leaving. Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:57.46,中文,,0,0,0,,-你知道哪有盐水么 -不知道 别管了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Did you find any saline? - No, leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我们叫齐所有人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We have to round everyone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.23,中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚说 时间不多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Julia said there isn't much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.60,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 如果没有生理盐水 我妻子会死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen, if I don't find that saline, my wife dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我就知道在这里 就等着我找来拿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I knew it! Like it was waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.26,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:13.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你妈妈在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your mom's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.93,中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚要我们把她抬到车子上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Julia wants our help loading up the buses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.12,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.39,中文,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得我们能出去么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you really think we're gonna get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 那个坑不稳定 但 是的 我们会出去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, the tunnels are freaky, but, yeah, we'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.18,中文,,0,0,0,,不是那些隧道的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:34.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 隧道后面的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's what's after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:39.00,中文,,0,0,0,,没有我妈妈 我还能回到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Am I just supposed to go back to my life in California?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我原本在加州的生活中去吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Without my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我怎么能够把她丢在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How can I go and just leave her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.26,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 她不在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, she's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.58,中文,,0,0,0,,安琪也不在了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Neither is Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.24,中文,,0,0,0,,她们可能被埋在切斯特磨坊镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They might be buried in Chester's Mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.67,中文,,0,0,0,,但她们一直都会陪在我们身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but they'll always be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:01.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我为什么参加训练营么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you know why I was going to boot camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.39,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么我要来这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why I'm here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:06.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜是你惹上麻烦了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I assumed you got into some kind of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我打了一个蠢丫头一拳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I punched some stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.03,中文,,0,0,0,,她的牙都被打出来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}girl in the mouth and knocked her tooth out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.32,中文,,0,0,0,,而她只是嘲笑了我的头发\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And all she did was make fun of my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:25.67,中文,,0,0,0,,现在一想到我是那么的介意就觉得自己好蠢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's just so... stupid to think how much I cared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:30.03,中文,,0,0,0,,-如果我不理她就好了 -不 穹顶要你来到这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- If I had just ignored her... - No, the dome wanted you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.82,中文,,0,0,0,,即使不这样 也有用其它的方式让你进来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It would have found another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我不在乎穹顶要什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't care what the dome wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我只要我的妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I just want my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.39,中文,,0,0,0,,困在穹顶的这些日子里 有时候我会想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sometimes I think, on Dome Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.96,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我和安琪能和我妈妈一起吃上一顿早午餐就好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if Angie and I just went to brunch with my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:50.39,中文,,0,0,0,,但那样的话 我就不能遇到你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But then I never would have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:56.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我妈妈死之前告诉我要勇敢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My mom told me before she died to be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.90,中文,,0,0,0,,但我现在一点也不勇敢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I just don't feel brave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:08.39,中文,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道跟着会发生什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know what's gonna happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.18,中文,,0,0,0,,但是 不管发生什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but, whatever's out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都会一起面对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we're gonna face it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.33,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:47.11,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.57,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.69,中文,,0,0,0,,波林 有新消息了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pauline, there's news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你开启的那条通道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The passage you opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们打算让大家从那里出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we're evacuating everyone through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.83,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 只要 只要你能坚持住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, if-if you can just hold on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就可以搏一把 就能带你去看医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we can try and get you to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我不行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我只会拖累我爱的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll only slow down the people I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.15,中文,,0,0,0,,再坚持一下就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.15,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.21,中文,,0,0,0,,不 这是穹顶想要的结局\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, this is what the dome wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:22.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是自作自受而已\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I paid for my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:28.27,中文,,0,0,0,,至少这一次 我可以一宿无梦 可以睡个好觉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}For once, I'll be able to sleep without dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:31.26,中文,,0,0,0,,不 现在我们有希望了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, there's hope now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.80,中文,,0,0,0,,多亏了你我们才能出去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're only getting out because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.39,中文,,0,0,0,,这很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.24,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔会平安无事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:42.69,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 太痛了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aah. This is so much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.85,中文,,0,0,0,,求你 求你发发好心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please... be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:48.39,中文,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.55,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 好心的女孩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah, sweet girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.21,中文,,0,0,0,,好心的女孩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sweet girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.94,中文,,0,0,0,,你能帮帮我 确保每个人都有位置吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can you help me and make sure everyone has a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.26,中文,,0,0,0,,-好 可以的 -谢谢 艾丹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Yeah, okay. - Thanks, Aidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.66,中文,,0,0,0,,下雨了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.53,中文,,0,0,0,,难道现在还不够遭吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If it wasn't enough of a mess already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.69,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶的收缩肯定会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome's contractions must be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.57,中文,,0,0,0,,让天气状况变遭 或是之类的什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}messing with the weather patterns... or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:28.39,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.04,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:32.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我都跟你说了一百遍了 我要留下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I told you a hundred times, I need to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.72,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈 我是那四个人之一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm one of the four hands, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.88,中文,,0,0,0,,-我必须帮忙 -我不是在询问你的意见 艾莉诺\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I have to help. - I'm not asking you, Eleanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:38.05,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿 诺瑞 帮我个忙 可以吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, hey, hey. Norrie, do me a favor, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:40.39,中文,,0,0,0,,上第一趟车 到了洞口后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get on this first bus, I'm really gonna need your help
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我非常需要你的帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}once we get to that crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.39,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.39,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.07,中文,,0,0,0,,好 快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.39,中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你看到安德里亚了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Have you seen Andrea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.39,中文,,0,0,0,,她去拿供给品了 她在洞口和我们汇合\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's getting supplies. She's gonna meet us at the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:08.10,中文,,0,0,0,,好 别发呆了 咱们走 快走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, don't stop. Let's go! Keep moving. Load up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.56,中文,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.11,中文,,0,0,0,,-嘿 波林呢 -她还在里面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Hey, where's Pauline? - She's still inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们在等吉姆从诊所回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're waiting for Jim to get back from the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.90,中文,,0,0,0,,他最好快点带着药剂回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, he'd better hurry with that saline.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你妹妹怎么样了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How is your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.71,中文,,0,0,0,,让我过去 我拿到药剂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let me through! I got the saline.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.71,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got it, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.72,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们得快点 -走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- We've got to hurry. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:24.02,中文,,0,0,0,,尽量帮助波林 然后我们得走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do what you can for Pauline, and then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.39,中文,,0,0,0,,一会见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:27.98,中文,,0,0,0,,宝贝 我拿到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Baby, I got it for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我找到你需要的东西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I found the stuff you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:32.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你 穹顶会保护我们的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I told you the dome was looking after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.21,中文,,0,0,0,,波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - Pauline,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我回来了 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm back, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:36.78,中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我不觉得疼了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}my pain is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.18,中文,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.47,中文,,0,0,0,,那真的太好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's good, that's real good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你会没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I told you it's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你爱我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.11,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你不用说对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't need to be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.97,中文,,0,0,0,,不用说对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}: You don't need to be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:01.77,中文,,0,0,0,,波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pauline?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.36,中文,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:13.95,中文,,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.65,中文,,0,0,0,,她的脉搏在变弱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her pulse is dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:18.47,中文,,0,0,0,,照顾好朱尼尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take care of Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pauline...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.90,中文,,0,0,0,,你才刚刚重回我身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I just got you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:01.73,中文,,0,0,0,,是你做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.39,中文,,0,0,0,,她说这是穹顶想要的结局\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She said it was what the dome wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.05,中文,,0,0,0,,她求我这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She begged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.30,中文,,0,0,0,,你总是知道该怎么做 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You always have the solutions, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我是为她好 我很抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was a kind thing to do. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你总是知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Always got something in your...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.82,中文,,0,0,0,,知道该怎么应对各种紧急情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in your back pocket for every emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:21.88,中文,,0,0,0,,那是她最后的要求了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was her last request.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.37,中文,,0,0,0,,然后你就可以杀了她吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, now you can kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.25,中文,,0,0,0,,不顾她还是我的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When it's my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.39,中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:29.26,中文,,0,0,0,,如果波林认为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if Pauline thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:31.27,中文,,0,0,0,,这是穹顶所想要的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that this is what the dome wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:33.69,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶想让我们一家人团聚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome wanted my family together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.40,中文,,0,0,0,,但是被你毁了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And you got in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.05,中文,,0,0,0,,走开 吉姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Walk away, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.04,中文,,0,0,0,,去找朱尼尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go find Junior,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.54,中文,,0,0,0,,带着他离开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我会永远想念我的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll miss my wife forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:10.08,中文,,0,0,0,,但没人会想念你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No one's gonna miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:26.89,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.10,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.63,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.77,中文,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.06,中文,,0,0,0,,山姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:41.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - You ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.89,中文,,0,0,0,,起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:45.14,中文,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.66,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, no. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我妈妈在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:53.89,中文,,0,0,0,,她死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:57.89,中文,,0,0,0,,-什么意思 -波林让丽贝卡帮她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What do you mean? - Pauline asked Rebecca to help her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.62,中文,,0,0,0,,结束她的生命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}end her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.97,中文,,0,0,0,,她太痛苦了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She was in so much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:07.33,中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆要向丽贝卡复仇了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim went after Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:10.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我试着阻止他 但是我失败了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I tried to stop him, I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:14.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 朱尼尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm so sorry, Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:36.89,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈那时是在跟我告别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mom was starting to say good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.31,0:22:40.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我早该明白的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:41.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得去找你的父亲 他完全失去理智了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've got to find your dad... he's gone crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.93,0:22:43.89,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们得去劝服他 -我为什么要这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- We've got to talk him down. - Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:47.50,中文,,0,0,0,,劝服对他来讲从来都没有用 只能和他做交易\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's no talking to him, there's only dealing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:51.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要画那幅画 波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why'd you paint that, Pauline?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:56.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我真希望你没画过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wish you hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:29.36,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dome...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:31.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我们做个交易\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll make you a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.65,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你能立刻把她带回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you bring her back right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:45.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我就答应不会伤害任何一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I won't murder every single one
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.66,0:23:47.46,中文,,0,0,0,,你的那些特殊的小朋友们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of your special little friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:53.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我就不撕碎茱莉亚的喉咙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I won't slit Julia's throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:57.74,中文,,0,0,0,,不一枪毙了芭比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}shoot Barbie in the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:02.26,中文,,0,0,0,,不活活烧死那些孩子们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or burn those kids alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.45,0:24:07.07,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.96,0:24:13.96,中文,,0,0,0,,给你三秒考虑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.47,0:24:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.89,0:24:51.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我会让你彻底的自由\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm gonna free you from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:56.96,中文,,0,0,0,,穿过穹顶 远离这里的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you can go right through that dome wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:02.31,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶会后悔它对我们所做的这一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it's gonna regret what it did to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.86,0:25:14.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.64,0:25:54.82,中文,,0,0,0,,这次和我们以前的计划一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is the same plan that we had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:57.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我们分成几个小组\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're all gonna break up into small groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.03,0:25:58.72,中文,,0,0,0,,一家人在一个组里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}keeping your family with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.72,0:26:01.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会一个一个的叫你们的名字 然后送你们下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We will call you forward one-by-one and get you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.56,0:26:03.75,中文,,0,0,0,,等到一个组的人齐了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Once your entire group is down,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.75,0:26:05.46,中文,,0,0,0,,乔和诺丽就带你们去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Joe and Norrie, here, will guide you into...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.46,0:26:06.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道这样做是安全的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How do you know this is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.00,0:26:13.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 因为我以前这么做过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know because I've done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.89,0:26:18.89,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道你们都很害怕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And, look, I know you're all scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.42,0:26:21.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我也知道我只是个陌生人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay? I-I-I know that I'm a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.89,0:26:24.68,中文,,0,0,0,,但是在过去的两周里 我们都为了这个小镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But for the last two weeks, we have fought together
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.68,0:26:26.31,中文,,0,0,0,,的生存而一起战斗过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for the survival of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.32,0:26:28.55,中文,,0,0,0,,现在 我需要你们相信我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But, right now, I need you to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.55,0:26:30.19,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们没有其他的选择了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}'Cause we don't have another choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.20,0:26:32.89,中文,,0,0,0,,如果继续待在这里 我们就只有死路一条\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If we stay here, we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:37.82,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.83,0:26:39.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一起离开这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.51,0:26:44.21,中文,,0,0,0,,卡洛琳 听着 我要你跟着我一起下去 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Carolyn, listen... I need you to go down with me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.21,0:26:45.89,中文,,0,0,0,,帮我让他们保持镇定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Help me keep everyone calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.53,0:26:47.89,中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚 亨特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Julia, Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.89,0:26:49.89,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 你们两个待在这上面好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, can I get you guys to stay at the top here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.89,0:26:51.73,中文,,0,0,0,,保持这里的秩序\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right? Keep everything orderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.74,0:26:53.89,中文,,0,0,0,,保证我们没有漏下任何人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Make sure we don't leave anyone behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.89,0:26:55.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我遗漏什么了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Am I forgetting anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.86,0:26:56.89,中文,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.89,0:26:58.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你该做的都做了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're doing exactly what you're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.00,0:27:00.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.99,0:27:02.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:06.13,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 大家准备好了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, you guys ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.13,0:27:07.62,中文,,0,0,0,,开始行动吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's do it.
