Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.17,0:29:04.59,中文,,0,0,0,,安德里亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Andrea?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.93,0:29:06.58,中文,,0,0,0,,在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In here.
