Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.78,0:30:44.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我给过穹顶机会 让它把波林还给我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. I gave the dome a chance to return her to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.13,0:30:45.67,中文,,0,0,0,,但是它拒绝了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but it declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.52,0:30:49.51,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你就遭殃了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which is bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.51,0:30:52.26,中文,,0,0,0,,杀了我 也不会让波林起死回生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Killing me... won't bring Pauline back.
