Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.72,0:33:58.09,中文,,0,0,0,,现在没时间了 芭比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie, there's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.10,0:33:59.90,中文,,0,0,0,,把他留给朱尼尔处理了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior's taking care of it.
