Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.99,0:34:14.68,中文,,0,0,0,,亨特 追上乔和诺瑞 告诉他们赶紧走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hunter, go up front with Joe and Norrie. Tell them to move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.69,0:34:16.49,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好吗 - 好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- All right? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.49,0:34:18.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我们也跟着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.76,0:34:20.76,中文,,0,0,0,,慢慢来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nice and slow.
