Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.09,0:35:13.60,中文,,0,0,0,,不 一定还有别的方法 我不会把你留在这的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, there's got to be another way. I'm not leaving you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.60,0:35:15.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你没有别的选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.42,0:35:16.91,中文,,0,0,0,,小镇需要你 你得快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The town needs your help, and fast...
