Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.58,0:35:42.51,中文,,0,0,0,,只要你能按照它的意愿行事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that if you do what it's asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.09,0:35:45.85,中文,,0,0,0,,它就会保护我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it will protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.09,0:36:00.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我会回来找你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm coming back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.13,0:36:01.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.19,0:36:28.19,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.57,0:36:31.20,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔 你不能丢下我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior, you can't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.42,0:36:47.70,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.65,0:36:50.94,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 茱莉亚在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie, where's Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:54.06,中文,,0,0,0,,她在后面 她让我先过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's coming. She sent me up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.42,0:36:58.87,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么大家都停下了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why's everybody stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.87,0:37:00.78,中文,,0,0,0,,没人知道该走哪条路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nobody knows which way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.78,0:37:02.30,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 我们应该走这条\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie, we need to go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.31,0:37:04.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我们看见有只蝴蝶飞去了这边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We saw the butterfly go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.01,0:37:04.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是个指示\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think it's a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.99,0:37:06.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我和乔都这么觉得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Both Joe and I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.67,0:37:11.08,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 我们走这边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, this is the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.08,0:37:12.09,中文,,0,0,0,,听到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.09,0:37:13.92,中文,,0,0,0,,大家都跟着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everybody follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.98,0:37:25.34,中文,,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.62,0:37:29.93,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比先走了 他会回来找我们的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie went ahead, he'll come back for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.32,0:37:33.20,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我们再想办法过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then we'll figure out a way across.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.09,0:38:23.97,中文,,0,0,0,,不 这里不该是条死胡同的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, this can't be all that's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.97,0:38:25.52,中文,,0,0,0,,- 不可能 - 这里面就只是个洞穴吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It can't be. - Is this a cave in?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.53,0:38:27.52,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 我们现在怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.09,0:38:29.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我 我也不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.78,0:38:33.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一路走来结果只是个死胡同吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We didn't come all this way for a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.38,0:38:36.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你妹啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.70,0:38:38.38,中文,,0,0,0,,听到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.38,0:38:40.77,中文,,0,0,0,,不管是谁在操控这一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whoever you are controlling all of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.78,0:38:44.02,中文,,0,0,0,,就不能告诉我们到底是怎么一回事吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}can you just talk to us and tell us what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.97,0:39:25.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你是怎么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.42,0:39:28.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我也什么都不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.09,0:39:35.09,中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么声音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.00,0:39:49.09,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.88,0:39:51.52,中文,,0,0,0,,跟着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.52,0:39:53.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're going home.
